## `templates/views/sales-points.html`

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Choix point de vente</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" th:href="@{/css/sales-points.css}">
</head>
<body>

<main class="screen">

    <header class="page-header">
        <img class="logo" th:src="@{/images/cetelem-logo.svg}" alt="Cetelem">

        <div class="language-selector">
            <button type="button" class="language-btn active">FR</button>
            <button type="button" class="language-btn">NL</button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="content-container">

        <section class="left-content">
            <h1>Connexion à<br>votre espace partenaire</h1>

            <h2>Votre point de vente</h2>

            <p>
                Vous devez choisir le point de vente dans lequel vous vous trouvez actuellement.
            </p>

            <form method="post" th:action="@{/sales-points/select}">
                <input type="hidden" th:name="${_csrf.parameterName}" th:value="${_csrf.token}">
                <input type="hidden" name="appId" th:value="${appId}">

                <div class="sales-list">
                    <label class="sales-option" th:each="sp, iter : ${salesPoints}">
                        <input type="radio"
                               name="salesPointId"
                               th:value="${sp.id}"
                               th:checked="${iter.index == 0}"
                               required>
                        <span th:text="${sp.label}">Sales Point</span>
                    </label>
                </div>

                <button class="confirm-btn" type="submit">
                    Confirmer <span>→</span>
                </button>
            </form>
        </section>

        <section class="right-illustration">
            <img class="background-pattern" th:src="@{/images/pattern-green.png}" alt="">
            <img class="mascot" th:src="@{/images/mascot.png}" alt="Mascot">
        </section>

    </section>

</main>

</body>
</html>
```

## `static/css/sales-points.css`

```css
* {
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

html,
body {
    margin: 0;
    min-height: 100%;
    font-family: "Open Sans", Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #071414;
}

.screen {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: #ffffff;
}

.page-header {
    height: 96px;
    padding: 16px 112px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: #ffffff;
}

.logo {
    width: 140px;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
}

.language-selector {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
}

.language-btn {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border: 0;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: transparent;
    color: #154734;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.language-btn.active {
    background: #154734;
    color: #ffffff;
}

.content-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 600px;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 96px);
}

.left-content {
    padding-left: 112px;
    padding-top: 72px;
    padding-right: 104px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 720px;
}

.left-content h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 48px;
    line-height: 1.15;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
}

.left-content h2 {
    margin: 12px 0 0;
    font-size: 40px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    font-weight: 300;
}

.left-content p {
    margin: 40px 0 40px;
    max-width: 560px;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: #3a3f45;
}

.sales-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
}

.sales-option {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #333333;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.sales-option input {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    accent-color: #154734;
}

.confirm-btn {
    margin-top: 40px;
    height: 48px;
    padding: 0 22px;
    border: 0;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #073331;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.confirm-btn span {
    margin-left: 8px;
}

.right-illustration {
    position: relative;
    width: 600px;
    height: 804px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-top-left-radius: 40px;
    background: #154734;
}

.background-pattern {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    z-index: 1;
}

.mascot {
    position: absolute;
    width: 700px;
    height: auto;
    right: -140px;
    bottom: -150px;
    z-index: 2;

    /* Use this only if mascot faces wrong direction */
    /* transform: scaleX(-1); */
}

/* Tablet */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .page-header {
        padding: 16px 40px;
    }

    .content-container {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 460px;
    }

    .left-content {
        padding-left: 40px;
        padding-right: 40px;
    }

    .right-illustration {
        width: 460px;
        height: 680px;
    }

    .mascot {
        width: 560px;
        right: -110px;
        bottom: -110px;
    }
}

/* Mobile */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header {
        height: 80px;
        padding: 16px 24px;
    }

    .logo {
        width: 120px;
    }

    .content-container {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
    }

    .right-illustration {
        order: -1;
        width: 100%;
        height: 360px;
        border-radius: 0;
    }

    .left-content {
        padding: 40px 24px;
        max-width: none;
    }

    .left-content h1 {
        font-size: 34px;
    }

    .left-content h2 {
        font-size: 28px;
    }

    .left-content p {
        margin: 32px 0;
        font-size: 15px;
    }

    .confirm-btn {
        width: 100%;
    }

    .mascot {
        width: 430px;
        right: -80px;
        bottom: -90px;
    }
}
